    "# 3. Currency Consistency Validation\n",
    "\n",
    "## Objective\n",
    "\n",
    "Financial metrics such as Sales Revenue, Sales Quota, and Inventory Value require consistent currency reporting to ensure accurate aggregation and comparison.\n",
    "\n",
    "This validation was performed to determine whether multiple currencies existed within the transactional datasets and whether currency conversion would be required during analysis."
