   "source": [
    "## Inventory Validation Summary\n",
    "\n",
    "### Key Findings\n",
    "\n",
    "- Inventory records represented periodic inventory snapshots.\n",
    "- Product and store inventory positions were recorded across multiple reporting dates.\n",
    "- Inventory status classifications were available for risk assessment.\n",
    "- Inventory values could be analysed using snapshot-based logic.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Business Impact\n",
    "\n",
    "Traditional cumulative inventory calculations would produce misleading results because records represent inventory positions rather than inventory movements.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Conclusion\n",
    "\n",
    "The Inventory dataset was modelled as a snapshot fact table, and inventory KPIs were developed using latest-date and snapshot-based calculations."
   ]
